{
  "chapter": 31,
  "chapter_summary": "第三十一回「月圆之约」。风四娘与连城璧在水月楼上面对四个一模一样的天宗主人小船，连城璧判断其中只有一个是真的，不敢贸然上船。忽然一条船驶来，连城璧与萧十一郎联手一击击倒黑衣人，不料此人竟被吓死。三人分头追踪逃跑的船只，风四娘独自驾船追踪，却被漩涡卷入湖中小楼。章横（水豹）从水中出现，风四娘用花盆砸晕他后进入小楼，竟遇见被认为已死的沈璧君。原来章横救起了跳湖的沈璧君，将她带至此地。章横解释他不让风四娘追踪是因为对方有三棱透骨针——天下最可怕的七种暗器之一。沈璧君终于问起萧十一郎，章横外出找食物时遭黑衣人袭击，三棱透骨针打入舌中，沈璧君果断割下其舌头救命。真正的天孙现身，风四娘企图用言语威胁但失败，与沈璧君联手出击却被一招击败。萧十一郎此时正在西湖北岸宝石山宝倜塔下。",
  "dialogues": [
    {
      "speaker": "char_qing_yi_tong_zi",
      "speaker_name": "青衣童子",
      "listener": "char_lian_cheng_bi",
      "text": "连公子在那里？请过来相见。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 31,
      "line_start": 10,
      "line_end": 12
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_feng_si_niang",
      "speaker_name": "风四娘",
      "listener": "char_lian_cheng_bi",
      "text": "你过不过去？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 31,
      "line_start": 16,
      "line_end": 16
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_feng_si_niang",
      "speaker_name": "风四娘",
      "listener": "char_lian_cheng_bi",
      "text": "为什么？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 31,
      "line_start": 20,
      "line_end": 20
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lian_cheng_bi",
      "speaker_name": "连城璧",
      "listener": "char_feng_si_niang",
      "text": "我一去就必死无疑。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 31,
      "line_start": 22,
      "line_end": 22
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lian_cheng_bi",
      "speaker_name": "连城璧",
      "listener": "char_feng_si_niang",
      "text": "这四人中只有一个是真的天宗主人。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 31,
      "line_start": 26,
      "line_end": 26
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_feng_si_niang",
      "speaker_name": "风四娘",
      "listener": "char_lian_cheng_bi",
      "text": "你也分不出他们的真假？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 31,
      "line_start": 28,
      "line_end": 28
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lian_cheng_bi",
      "speaker_name": "连城璧",
      "listener": "char_feng_si_niang",
      "text": "所以我不能过去，我根本不知道应该上哪条船。",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 31,
      "line_start": 30,
      "line_end": 31
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_feng_si_niang",
      "speaker_name": "风四娘",
      "listener": "char_lian_cheng_bi",
      "text": "难道你上错了船就非死不可？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 31,
      "line_start": 34,
      "line_end": 34
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lian_cheng_bi",
      "speaker_name": "连城璧",
      "listener": "char_feng_si_niang",
      "text": "这约会是花如玉订的，他们之间一定已约好了见面的法子。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 31,
      "line_start": 36,
      "line_end": 37
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_feng_si_niang",
      "speaker_name": "风四娘",
      "listener": "char_lian_cheng_bi",
      "text": "花如玉没有告诉你？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 31,
      "line_start": 40,
      "line_end": 40
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lian_cheng_bi",
      "speaker_name": "连城璧",
      "listener": "char_feng_si_niang",
      "text": "没有。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 31,
      "line_start": 42,
      "line_end": 42
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_feng_si_niang",
      "speaker_name": "风四娘",
      "listener": "char_lian_cheng_bi",
      "text": "难怪他临死前还说，你若杀了他，必定会后悔。",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 31,
      "line_start": 44,
      "line_end": 45
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_feng_si_niang",
      "speaker_name": "风四娘",
      "listener": "char_lian_cheng_bi",
      "text": "世上有很多事都是这样子的，你若坚持不肯过去，他就只好过来了。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 31,
      "line_start": 50,
      "line_end": 52
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lian_cheng_bi",
      "speaker_name": "连城璧",
      "listener": "char_feng_si_niang",
      "text": "你知道来的人是真是假？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 31,
      "line_start": 54,
      "line_end": 54
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_feng_si_niang",
      "speaker_name": "风四娘",
      "listener": "char_lian_cheng_bi",
      "text": "不管他是真是假，我们都不妨先到灯下去等着他。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 31,
      "line_start": 56,
      "line_end": 56
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lian_cheng_bi",
      "speaker_name": "连城璧",
      "listener": "char_xiao_shi_yi_lang",
      "text": "这人绝不是天孙。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 31,
      "line_start": 94,
      "line_end": 94
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_shi_yi_lang",
      "speaker_name": "萧十一郎",
      "listener": "char_lian_cheng_bi",
      "text": "哦？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 31,
      "line_start": 96,
      "line_end": 96
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lian_cheng_bi",
      "speaker_name": "连城璧",
      "listener": "char_xiao_shi_yi_lang",
      "text": "我见过他出手，以他的武功，我们纵然全力而击，三十招内也胜不了他。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 31,
      "line_start": 98,
      "line_end": 99
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_feng_si_niang",
      "speaker_name": "风四娘",
      "listener": "char_xiao_shi_yi_lang",
      "text": "这人已死了。",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "chapter": 31,
      "line_start": 106,
      "line_end": 106
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lian_cheng_bi",
      "speaker_name": "连城璧",
      "listener": "char_feng_si_niang",
      "text": "他怎么会死？我的出手并不太重。",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 31,
      "line_start": 110,
      "line_end": 110
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_shi_yi_lang",
      "speaker_name": "萧十一郎",
      "listener": "char_feng_si_niang",
      "text": "我也想留下他的活口。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 31,
      "line_start": 112,
      "line_end": 112
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_feng_si_niang",
      "speaker_name": "风四娘",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "看来他……他好像是被吓死的。",
      "tone": "恐惧",
      "chapter": 31,
      "line_start": 114,
      "line_end": 114
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_feng_si_niang",
      "speaker_name": "风四娘",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "他们一定已发现不对了，竟连这孩子一起杀了灭口。",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 31,
      "line_start": 128,
      "line_end": 130
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lian_cheng_bi",
      "speaker_name": "连城璧",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "他们这一走，要想再查出他们的行踪，只怕已难如登天。",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 31,
      "line_start": 132,
      "line_end": 133
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_shi_yi_lang",
      "speaker_name": "萧十一郎",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "所以我们一定要追。",
      "tone": "坚定",
      "chapter": 31,
      "line_start": 136,
      "line_end": 136
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_feng_si_niang",
      "speaker_name": "风四娘",
      "listener": "char_xiao_shi_yi_lang",
      "text": "怎么追？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 31,
      "line_start": 138,
      "line_end": 138
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_shi_yi_lang",
      "speaker_name": "萧十一郎",
      "listener": "char_feng_si_niang",
      "text": "中间一条船走得很慢，你坐下面的这条船去盯住他。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 31,
      "line_start": 140,
      "line_end": 141
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lian_cheng_bi",
      "speaker_name": "连城璧",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "我追左边的一条。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 31,
      "line_start": 144,
      "line_end": 144
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_shi_yi_lang",
      "speaker_name": "萧十一郎",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "只要追出了他们的下落，就立刻回来，千万不要轻举妄动。",
      "tone": "严肃",
      "chapter": 31,
      "line_start": 146,
      "line_end": 147
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_feng_si_niang",
      "speaker_name": "风四娘",
      "listener": "char_xiao_shi_yi_lang",
      "text": "你……你会在这里等我？",
      "tone": "担心",
      "chapter": 31,
      "line_start": 150,
      "line_end": 150
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_shi_yi_lang",
      "speaker_name": "萧十一郎",
      "listener": "char_feng_si_niang",
      "text": "不管有没有消息，明天中午以前，我一定回来。",
      "tone": "承诺",
      "chapter": 31,
      "line_start": 152,
      "line_end": 152
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_feng_si_niang",
      "speaker_name": "风四娘",
      "listener": "char_zhang_heng",
      "text": "我还以为是水鬼在找替身，想不到是你。",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 31,
      "line_start": 248,
      "line_end": 250
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhang_heng",
      "speaker_name": "章横",
      "listener": "char_feng_si_niang",
      "text": "我也想不到大名鼎鼎的风四娘居然还记得我。",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 31,
      "line_start": 252,
      "line_end": 253
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_feng_si_niang",
      "speaker_name": "风四娘",
      "listener": "char_zhang_heng",
      "text": "你知道我就是大名鼎鼎的风四娘？",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 31,
      "line_start": 256,
      "line_end": 256
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhang_heng",
      "speaker_name": "章横",
      "listener": "char_feng_si_niang",
      "text": "我当然知道。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 31,
      "line_start": 258,
      "line_end": 258
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_feng_si_niang",
      "speaker_name": "风四娘",
      "listener": "char_zhang_heng",
      "text": "这地方是你的家？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 31,
      "line_start": 260,
      "line_end": 260
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhang_heng",
      "speaker_name": "章横",
      "listener": "char_feng_si_niang",
      "text": "这是西湖，不是太湖，我只不过临时找了这屋子住着。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 31,
      "line_start": 262,
      "line_end": 263
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_feng_si_niang",
      "speaker_name": "风四娘",
      "listener": "char_zhang_heng",
      "text": "那么这就是你临时的家。",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 31,
      "line_start": 266,
      "line_end": 266
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhang_heng",
      "speaker_name": "章横",
      "listener": "char_feng_si_niang",
      "text": "可以这么样说。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 31,
      "line_start": 268,
      "line_end": 268
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_feng_si_niang",
      "speaker_name": "风四娘",
      "listener": "char_zhang_heng",
      "text": "你把我带到你临时的家，是不是想要我做你临时的老婆？",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 31,
      "line_start": 270,
      "line_end": 271
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhang_heng",
      "speaker_name": "章横",
      "listener": "char_feng_si_niang",
      "text": "我不是这意思。",
      "tone": "慌张",
      "chapter": 31,
      "line_start": 280,
      "line_end": 280
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_feng_si_niang",
      "speaker_name": "风四娘",
      "listener": "char_zhang_heng",
      "text": "不管你是什么意思，这地方总是你的家，你这做主人的为什么还不上来招呼客人？",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 31,
      "line_start": 282,
      "line_end": 283
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhang_heng",
      "speaker_name": "章横",
      "listener": "char_feng_si_niang",
      "text": "我就上来。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 31,
      "line_start": 286,
      "line_end": 286
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_feng_si_niang",
      "speaker_name": "风四娘",
      "listener": "char_zhang_heng",
      "text": "想不到你不但水性高，壁虎功也这么高。",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 31,
      "line_start": 298,
      "line_end": 298
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhang_heng",
      "speaker_name": "章横",
      "listener": "char_feng_si_niang",
      "text": "我只不过……",
      "tone": "慌张",
      "chapter": 31,
      "line_start": 300,
      "line_end": 300
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_feng_si_niang",
      "speaker_name": "风四娘",
      "listener": "char_zhang_heng",
      "text": "在水里我虽然是个旱鸭子，可是一到了岸上，我随时都能让你变成一个死鸭子。",
      "tone": "得意",
      "chapter": 31,
      "line_start": 310,
      "line_end": 311
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_feng_si_niang",
      "speaker_name": "风四娘",
      "listener": "char_shen_bi_jun",
      "text": "沈璧君。",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "chapter": 31,
      "line_start": 328,
      "line_end": 328
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_feng_si_niang",
      "speaker_name": "风四娘",
      "listener": "char_shen_bi_jun",
      "text": "你……你怎么会到这里来的？",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "chapter": 31,
      "line_start": 336,
      "line_end": 336
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shen_bi_jun",
      "speaker_name": "沈璧君",
      "listener": "char_feng_si_niang",
      "text": "我没有死。",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 31,
      "line_start": 346,
      "line_end": 346
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_feng_si_niang",
      "speaker_name": "风四娘",
      "listener": "char_shen_bi_jun",
      "text": "我看得出。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 31,
      "line_start": 348,
      "line_end": 348
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shen_bi_jun",
      "speaker_name": "沈璧君",
      "listener": "char_feng_si_niang",
      "text": "你是不是很奇怪？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 31,
      "line_start": 350,
      "line_end": 350
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_feng_si_niang",
      "speaker_name": "风四娘",
      "listener": "char_shen_bi_jun",
      "text": "我……我很高兴。",
      "tone": "欣慰",
      "chapter": 31,
      "line_start": 352,
      "line_end": 352
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shen_bi_jun",
      "speaker_name": "沈璧君",
      "listener": "char_feng_si_niang",
      "text": "其实我自己也没有想到，居然会有人救了我。",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 31,
      "line_start": 360,
      "line_end": 361
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_feng_si_niang",
      "speaker_name": "风四娘",
      "listener": "char_shen_bi_jun",
      "text": "是谁救了你？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 31,
      "line_start": 364,
      "line_end": 364
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shen_bi_jun",
      "speaker_name": "沈璧君",
      "listener": "char_feng_si_niang",
      "text": "章横。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 31,
      "line_start": 366,
      "line_end": 366
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_feng_si_niang",
      "speaker_name": "风四娘",
      "listener": "char_shen_bi_jun",
      "text": "章横？",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "chapter": 31,
      "line_start": 368,
      "line_end": 368
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shen_bi_jun",
      "speaker_name": "沈璧君",
      "listener": "char_feng_si_niang",
      "text": "我相信你一定也见过他的，昨天他也在水月楼上。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 31,
      "line_start": 376,
      "line_end": 377
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_feng_si_niang",
      "speaker_name": "风四娘",
      "listener": "char_shen_bi_jun",
      "text": "我见过他，第一个青衣人忽然失踪的时候，叫得最起劲的就是他。",
      "tone": "苦笑",
      "chapter": 31,
      "line_start": 380,
      "line_end": 381
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shen_bi_jun",
      "speaker_name": "沈璧君",
      "listener": "char_feng_si_niang",
      "text": "他的确是个很热心的人，先父在世的时候就认得他，还救过他一次，所以他一直都在找机会报恩。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 31,
      "line_start": 384,
      "line_end": 385
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_feng_si_niang",
      "speaker_name": "风四娘",
      "listener": "char_shen_bi_jun",
      "text": "他救你真的是为了报恩？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 31,
      "line_start": 388,
      "line_end": 388
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shen_bi_jun",
      "speaker_name": "沈璧君",
      "listener": "char_feng_si_niang",
      "text": "他一直对那天发生在水月楼的事觉得怀疑，所以别人都走了后，他还想暗中回来查明究竟。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 31,
      "line_start": 390,
      "line_end": 391
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_feng_si_niang",
      "speaker_name": "风四娘",
      "listener": "char_shen_bi_jun",
      "text": "他回来的时候，就是你跳下水的时候？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 31,
      "line_start": 394,
      "line_end": 394
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shen_bi_jun",
      "speaker_name": "沈璧君",
      "listener": "char_feng_si_niang",
      "text": "那时他已在水里呆了很久，后来我才知道，一天之中，他总有几个时辰是泡在水里的，他觉得在水里远比在岸上还舒服。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 31,
      "line_start": 396,
      "line_end": 397
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_feng_si_niang",
      "speaker_name": "风四娘",
      "listener": "char_shen_bi_jun",
      "text": "他救了你后，为什么不送你回去？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 31,
      "line_start": 404,
      "line_end": 404
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shen_bi_jun",
      "speaker_name": "沈璧君",
      "listener": "char_feng_si_niang",
      "text": "回去？回到哪里去？水月楼又不是我的家。",
      "tone": "悲伤",
      "chapter": 31,
      "line_start": 406,
      "line_end": 406
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_feng_si_niang",
      "speaker_name": "风四娘",
      "listener": "char_shen_bi_jun",
      "text": "可是你……你难道真的不愿再见我们？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 31,
      "line_start": 410,
      "line_end": 410
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shen_bi_jun",
      "speaker_name": "沈璧君",
      "listener": "char_feng_si_niang",
      "text": "我知道你们一定在为我担心，我……我也在相信着你们，可是我却宁愿让你们认为我已死了，因为……这世界上若是少了我这么样一个人，你们反而会活得更好些。",
      "tone": "悲伤",
      "chapter": 31,
      "line_start": 412,
      "line_end": 413
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shen_bi_jun",
      "speaker_name": "沈璧君",
      "listener": "char_feng_si_niang",
      "text": "可是章横还是怕你们担心，一定要去看看你们，他去了很久。他实在是个很热心的人。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 31,
      "line_start": 420,
      "line_end": 422
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shen_bi_jun",
      "speaker_name": "沈璧君",
      "listener": "char_feng_si_niang",
      "text": "我刚才迷迷糊糊的睡了一下子，好像听见外面有很响的声音。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 31,
      "line_start": 428,
      "line_end": 429
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_feng_si_niang",
      "speaker_name": "风四娘",
      "listener": "char_shen_bi_jun",
      "text": "嗯。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 31,
      "line_start": 432,
      "line_end": 432
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shen_bi_jun",
      "speaker_name": "沈璧君",
      "listener": "char_feng_si_niang",
      "text": "那是什么声音？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 31,
      "line_start": 434,
      "line_end": 434
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhang_heng",
      "speaker_name": "章横",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "那是一只死鸭子被旱鸭子打得掉下水的声音。",
      "tone": "苦笑",
      "chapter": 31,
      "line_start": 436,
      "line_end": 437
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shen_bi_jun",
      "speaker_name": "沈璧君",
      "listener": "char_zhang_heng",
      "text": "你头上为什么会肿了一大块？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 31,
      "line_start": 446,
      "line_end": 446
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhang_heng",
      "speaker_name": "章横",
      "listener": "char_shen_bi_jun",
      "text": "也不为什么，只不过因为有人想比一比。",
      "tone": "苦笑",
      "chapter": 31,
      "line_start": 448,
      "line_end": 448
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shen_bi_jun",
      "speaker_name": "沈璧君",
      "listener": "char_zhang_heng",
      "text": "比什么？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 31,
      "line_start": 450,
      "line_end": 450
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhang_heng",
      "speaker_name": "章横",
      "listener": "char_shen_bi_jun",
      "text": "比一比是我的头硬？还是花盆硬？",
      "tone": "苦笑",
      "chapter": 31,
      "line_start": 452,
      "line_end": 452
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_feng_si_niang",
      "speaker_name": "风四娘",
      "listener": "char_shen_bi_jun",
      "text": "你猜猜究竟是花盆硬？还是他的头硬？",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 31,
      "line_start": 458,
      "line_end": 458
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shen_bi_jun",
      "speaker_name": "沈璧君",
      "listener": "char_feng_si_niang",
      "text": "是花盆硬。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 31,
      "line_start": 460,
      "line_end": 460
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_feng_si_niang",
      "speaker_name": "风四娘",
      "listener": "char_shen_bi_jun",
      "text": "若是花盆硬，为什么花盆会被他撞得少了一个角，他头上反而多了一个角？",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 31,
      "line_start": 462,
      "line_end": 463
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhang_heng",
      "speaker_name": "章横",
      "listener": "char_feng_si_niang",
      "text": "现在我总算明白了一件事。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 31,
      "line_start": 470,
      "line_end": 470
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_feng_si_niang",
      "speaker_name": "风四娘",
      "listener": "char_zhang_heng",
      "text": "什么事？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 31,
      "line_start": 472,
      "line_end": 472
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhang_heng",
      "speaker_name": "章横",
      "listener": "char_feng_si_niang",
      "text": "我现在总算才明白，江湖中为什么会有那么多人把你当做女妖怪。",
      "tone": "苦笑",
      "chapter": 31,
      "line_start": 474,
      "line_end": 475
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_feng_si_niang",
      "speaker_name": "风四娘",
      "listener": "char_zhang_heng",
      "text": "现在我却还有件事不明白。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 31,
      "line_start": 478,
      "line_end": 478
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhang_heng",
      "speaker_name": "章横",
      "listener": "char_feng_si_niang",
      "text": "什么事？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 31,
      "line_start": 480,
      "line_end": 480
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_feng_si_niang",
      "speaker_name": "风四娘",
      "listener": "char_zhang_heng",
      "text": "你为什么不让我去追那条船？",
      "tone": "严肃",
      "chapter": 31,
      "line_start": 482,
      "line_end": 482
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhang_heng",
      "speaker_name": "章横",
      "listener": "char_feng_si_niang",
      "text": "因为我不想看着你死在水里。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 31,
      "line_start": 484,
      "line_end": 484
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_feng_si_niang",
      "speaker_name": "风四娘",
      "listener": "char_zhang_heng",
      "text": "难道我还应该谢谢你？",
      "tone": "嘲讽",
      "chapter": 31,
      "line_start": 486,
      "line_end": 486
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhang_heng",
      "speaker_name": "章横",
      "listener": "char_feng_si_niang",
      "text": "你知不知道那船夫和那孩子是怎么死的？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 31,
      "line_start": 488,
      "line_end": 488
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_feng_si_niang",
      "speaker_name": "风四娘",
      "listener": "char_zhang_heng",
      "text": "你知道。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 31,
      "line_start": 490,
      "line_end": 490
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhang_heng",
      "speaker_name": "章横",
      "listener": "char_feng_si_niang",
      "text": "这暗器就是我从他们身上取出来的。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 31,
      "line_start": 492,
      "line_end": 492
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_feng_si_niang",
      "speaker_name": "风四娘",
      "listener": "char_zhang_heng",
      "text": "三棱透骨针？",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "chapter": 31,
      "line_start": 496,
      "line_end": 496
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhang_heng",
      "speaker_name": "章横",
      "listener": "char_feng_si_niang",
      "text": "我知道你一定能认得出的。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 31,
      "line_start": 498,
      "line_end": 498
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_feng_si_niang",
      "speaker_name": "风四娘",
      "listener": "char_zhang_heng",
      "text": "就算我没吃过猪肉，至少总还看见过猪走路。",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 31,
      "line_start": 500,
      "line_end": 500
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhang_heng",
      "speaker_name": "章横",
      "listener": "char_feng_si_niang",
      "text": "这种暗器通常都是用机簧发射，就算在水里，也能打出去三五丈远，我们在水底下最怕遇见的，就是这种暗器。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 31,
      "line_start": 508,
      "line_end": 509
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_feng_si_niang",
      "speaker_name": "风四娘",
      "listener": "char_zhang_heng",
      "text": "我一向很少在水底下，我既不是水鬼，也不是鱼。",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 31,
      "line_start": 512,
      "line_end": 512
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhang_heng",
      "speaker_name": "章横",
      "listener": "char_feng_si_niang",
      "text": "若是在水面上，这种暗器远在七八丈外，也能取人的性命。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 31,
      "line_start": 514,
      "line_end": 515
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_feng_si_niang",
      "speaker_name": "风四娘",
      "listener": "char_zhang_heng",
      "text": "身上带着这种暗器的人，就在我追的那条船上？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 31,
      "line_start": 518,
      "line_end": 518
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_feng_si_niang",
      "speaker_name": "风四娘",
      "listener": "char_zhang_heng",
      "text": "难道你以为我就怕了这种暗器？若连这几根钉子都躲不过，我还算什么女妖怪？",
      "tone": "冷笑",
      "chapter": 31,
      "line_start": 522,
      "line_end": 523
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_feng_si_niang",
      "speaker_name": "风四娘",
      "listener": "char_shen_bi_jun",
      "text": "你为什么不问问我，他在哪里？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 31,
      "line_start": 542,
      "line_end": 543
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_feng_si_niang",
      "speaker_name": "风四娘",
      "listener": "char_shen_bi_jun",
      "text": "这地方虽不错，你还是不能在这里呆一辈子的，该走的迟早总是要走，你难道忘了这是谁说的话？",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 31,
      "line_start": 548,
      "line_end": 549
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhang_heng",
      "speaker_name": "章横",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你们饿不饿？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 31,
      "line_start": 554,
      "line_end": 554
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_feng_si_niang",
      "speaker_name": "风四娘",
      "listener": "char_zhang_heng",
      "text": "饿得要命。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 31,
      "line_start": 556,
      "line_end": 556
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhang_heng",
      "speaker_name": "章横",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "我去找点东西来给你们吃，随便换身衣服，来回一趟至少也得半个时辰。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 31,
      "line_start": 558,
      "line_end": 559
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_feng_si_niang",
      "speaker_name": "风四娘",
      "listener": "char_zhang_heng",
      "text": "你慢慢的找，慢慢的换，我们一点也不急。",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 31,
      "line_start": 562,
      "line_end": 562
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shen_bi_jun",
      "speaker_name": "沈璧君",
      "listener": "char_feng_si_niang",
      "text": "他……他在哪里？为什么没有跟你在一起？",
      "tone": "担心",
      "chapter": 31,
      "line_start": 566,
      "line_end": 567
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_feng_si_niang",
      "speaker_name": "风四娘",
      "listener": "char_zhang_heng",
      "text": "你怎么样了？",
      "tone": "慌张",
      "chapter": 31,
      "line_start": 586,
      "line_end": 586
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shen_bi_jun",
      "speaker_name": "沈璧君",
      "listener": "char_zhang_heng",
      "text": "你能不能张开嘴？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 31,
      "line_start": 592,
      "line_end": 592
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_feng_si_niang",
      "speaker_name": "风四娘",
      "listener": "char_zhang_heng",
      "text": "为什么连嘴都张不开？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 31,
      "line_start": 596,
      "line_end": 596
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tian_sun",
      "speaker_name": "黑衣人",
      "listener": "char_feng_si_niang",
      "text": "你想不想救他的命？",
      "tone": "淡然",
      "chapter": 31,
      "line_start": 606,
      "line_end": 606
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tian_sun",
      "speaker_name": "黑衣人",
      "listener": "char_feng_si_niang",
      "text": "好，先割下他的舌头，再迟就来不及了。",
      "tone": "淡然",
      "chapter": 31,
      "line_start": 610,
      "line_end": 610
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_feng_si_niang",
      "speaker_name": "风四娘",
      "listener": "char_shen_bi_jun",
      "text": "你……你竟能下得了手。",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "chapter": 31,
      "line_start": 622,
      "line_end": 622
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shen_bi_jun",
      "speaker_name": "沈璧君",
      "listener": "char_feng_si_niang",
      "text": "我不能不下手，因为我不能看着他死。",
      "tone": "坚定",
      "chapter": 31,
      "line_start": 624,
      "line_end": 624
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tian_sun",
      "speaker_name": "黑衣人",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "现在你们已可跟我走了。",
      "tone": "淡然",
      "chapter": 31,
      "line_start": 630,
      "line_end": 631
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_feng_si_niang",
      "speaker_name": "风四娘",
      "listener": "char_tian_sun",
      "text": "跟你走？你是什么人？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 31,
      "line_start": 634,
      "line_end": 634
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tian_sun",
      "speaker_name": "黑衣人",
      "listener": "char_feng_si_niang",
      "text": "你应该知道我是什么人。",
      "tone": "淡然",
      "chapter": 31,
      "line_start": 636,
      "line_end": 636
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_feng_si_niang",
      "speaker_name": "风四娘",
      "listener": "char_tian_sun",
      "text": "你就是天孙？真的天孙？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 31,
      "line_start": 638,
      "line_end": 638
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tian_sun",
      "speaker_name": "黑衣人",
      "listener": "char_feng_si_niang",
      "text": "无相天孙，身外化身，真即是假，假即是真。",
      "tone": "淡然",
      "chapter": 31,
      "line_start": 640,
      "line_end": 640
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_feng_si_niang",
      "speaker_name": "风四娘",
      "listener": "char_tian_sun",
      "text": "你知不知道我是谁？",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 31,
      "line_start": 642,
      "line_end": 642
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tian_sun",
      "speaker_name": "黑衣人",
      "listener": "char_feng_si_niang",
      "text": "风四娘。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 31,
      "line_start": 644,
      "line_end": 644
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_feng_si_niang",
      "speaker_name": "风四娘",
      "listener": "char_tian_sun",
      "text": "你既然知道我是谁，又看过我的脸，至少也该让我看看你。",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 31,
      "line_start": 646,
      "line_end": 647
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tian_sun",
      "speaker_name": "黑衣人",
      "listener": "char_feng_si_niang",
      "text": "你迟早总看得到的。",
      "tone": "淡然",
      "chapter": 31,
      "line_start": 650,
      "line_end": 650
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_feng_si_niang",
      "speaker_name": "风四娘",
      "listener": "char_tian_sun",
      "text": "你先让我看看，我才跟你走。",
      "tone": "撒娇",
      "chapter": 31,
      "line_start": 652,
      "line_end": 652
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tian_sun",
      "speaker_name": "黑衣人",
      "listener": "char_feng_si_niang",
      "text": "否则呢？",
      "tone": "淡然",
      "chapter": 31,
      "line_start": 654,
      "line_end": 654
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_feng_si_niang",
      "speaker_name": "风四娘",
      "listener": "char_tian_sun",
      "text": "你不肯答应我的事，我当然也不肯答应你。",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 31,
      "line_start": 656,
      "line_end": 656
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tian_sun",
      "speaker_name": "黑衣人",
      "listener": "char_feng_si_niang",
      "text": "你真的不走？",
      "tone": "淡然",
      "chapter": 31,
      "line_start": 658,
      "line_end": 658
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_feng_si_niang",
      "speaker_name": "风四娘",
      "listener": "char_tian_sun",
      "text": "你要我走，我就偏偏要坐在这里，看你怎么样？",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 31,
      "line_start": 660,
      "line_end": 660
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tian_sun",
      "speaker_name": "黑衣人",
      "listener": "char_feng_si_niang",
      "text": "你要看看我能把你怎么样？",
      "tone": "冷笑",
      "chapter": 31,
      "line_start": 666,
      "line_end": 666
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_feng_si_niang",
      "speaker_name": "风四娘",
      "listener": "char_tian_sun",
      "text": "嗯。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 31,
      "line_start": 668,
      "line_end": 668
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tian_sun",
      "speaker_name": "黑衣人",
      "listener": "char_feng_si_niang",
      "text": "好，你看着吧。",
      "tone": "冷笑",
      "chapter": 31,
      "line_start": 670,
      "line_end": 670
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_feng_si_niang",
      "speaker_name": "风四娘",
      "listener": "char_tian_sun",
      "text": "你敢对我无礼？",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 31,
      "line_start": 676,
      "line_end": 676
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tian_sun",
      "speaker_name": "黑衣人",
      "listener": "char_feng_si_niang",
      "text": "我不但要对你无礼，而且还要很无礼。",
      "tone": "冷笑",
      "chapter": 31,
      "line_start": 678,
      "line_end": 678
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_feng_si_niang",
      "speaker_name": "风四娘",
      "listener": "char_tian_sun",
      "text": "你们这四个真真假假的天孙中，刚才是不是有一个上了水月楼？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 31,
      "line_start": 680,
      "line_end": 682
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tian_sun",
      "speaker_name": "黑衣人",
      "listener": "char_feng_si_niang",
      "text": "嗯。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 31,
      "line_start": 684,
      "line_end": 684
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_feng_si_niang",
      "speaker_name": "风四娘",
      "listener": "char_tian_sun",
      "text": "你知不知道他现在怎么样了？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 31,
      "line_start": 686,
      "line_end": 686
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tian_sun",
      "speaker_name": "黑衣人",
      "listener": "char_feng_si_niang",
      "text": "死了。",
      "tone": "淡然",
      "chapter": 31,
      "line_start": 688,
      "line_end": 688
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_feng_si_niang",
      "speaker_name": "风四娘",
      "listener": "char_tian_sun",
      "text": "你知不知道他怎么死的？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 31,
      "line_start": 690,
      "line_end": 690
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_feng_si_niang",
      "speaker_name": "风四娘",
      "listener": "char_tian_sun",
      "text": "他是吓死的。你看见过被吓死的人没有？我可以保证；一个人无论怎么样死法，都没有吓死的可怕。",
      "tone": "嘲讽",
      "chapter": 31,
      "line_start": 694,
      "line_end": 696
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tian_sun",
      "speaker_name": "黑衣人",
      "listener": "char_feng_si_niang",
      "text": "哦？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 31,
      "line_start": 700,
      "line_end": 700
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_feng_si_niang",
      "speaker_name": "风四娘",
      "listener": "char_tian_sun",
      "text": "你知不知道他是怎么样被吓死的？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 31,
      "line_start": 702,
      "line_end": 702
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_feng_si_niang",
      "speaker_name": "风四娘",
      "listener": "char_tian_sun",
      "text": "因为他做梦也想不到，竟连一招都招架不住，我们一出手，他就已倒下。",
      "tone": "得意",
      "chapter": 31,
      "line_start": 706,
      "line_end": 707
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_feng_si_niang",
      "speaker_name": "风四娘",
      "listener": "char_tian_sun",
      "text": "你的武功比他怎么样？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 31,
      "line_start": 712,
      "line_end": 713
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tian_sun",
      "speaker_name": "黑衣人",
      "listener": "char_feng_si_niang",
      "text": "差不多。",
      "tone": "淡然",
      "chapter": 31,
      "line_start": 716,
      "line_end": 716
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_feng_si_niang",
      "speaker_name": "风四娘",
      "listener": "char_tian_sun",
      "text": "这里虽不是水月楼，可是你只要再往前走一步，我就要你立毙掌下。",
      "tone": "冷笑",
      "chapter": 31,
      "line_start": 718,
      "line_end": 719
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tian_sun",
      "speaker_name": "黑衣人",
      "listener": "char_feng_si_niang",
      "text": "真的？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 31,
      "line_start": 722,
      "line_end": 722
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_feng_si_niang",
      "speaker_name": "风四娘",
      "listener": "char_tian_sun",
      "text": "当然是真的。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 31,
      "line_start": 724,
      "line_end": 724
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tian_sun",
      "speaker_name": "黑衣人",
      "listener": "char_feng_si_niang",
      "text": "只要我再往前一步，我就必死无疑？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 31,
      "line_start": 726,
      "line_end": 726
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_feng_si_niang",
      "speaker_name": "风四娘",
      "listener": "char_tian_sun",
      "text": "不错。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 31,
      "line_start": 728,
      "line_end": 728
    }
